column1: PROJECT_DESCRIPTION=Biodiversity trawl survey for the Passamaquoddy Bay and Fundy Isles area
MISSION=Unique mission identification code for each trawl year
SETNO=Unique identification code for each set within a trawl year

FISH_LENGTH=Measurement in mm of total length for all fish species, shell width for bivalves except scallop species where shell height measured and carapace length from posterior portion of thorax to eye socket in lobster
